---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="BibleStudy — A Custom Study Bible">
  <h1>BibleStudy</h1>
  <p class="provenance">
    A custom-translated study Bible with interlinear, chronology, maps, slides, and song.
    Generated by BibleStudyTool and built statically with Astro.
  </p>
  <h2>Open a chapter</h2>
  <p>
    The site is in early scaffold — Genesis 1 is the first chapter wired end-to-end.
    More chapters land as the BibleStudyTool emitter generates them.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/genesis/1/`}>Genesis 1</a></li>
  </ul>
  <h2>What's here</h2>
  <p>
    Each chapter page is the canonical reading unit. Verses are inline-expandable —
    tap a verse number to reveal interlinear, exegesis, cross-references, places,
    chronology, slides, and song panels for that verse. Translations are user-selectable
    from the Settings page (defaults: ASV + BSB + KJV + custom LLM).
  </p>
</Base>
